Hi Ann, yes Erland Babcock. I hear the name Erland mentioned from time to time I imagine he is very busy. I tried a new session at a higher volume. This time there were mentions of other &#39;stations&#39; or control points. They seem to be testing or comparing reception. I hear what might be a new word &#39;recept&#39; like in reception. I hear this mainly as a low male voice like a weak radio signal.



&quot;Choose Amsterdam to recept David&#39;s signal&quot;



The other chatter indicates they are somehow tracking the output of the optical microphone, they call it a SeptiCom.



Dave



